title: Should YOU Go Vegan? Bananiac Responds to Russell Brand The Trews
tags: ['bananiac', 'Should I Become A Vegan? Russell Brand The Trews Comments (E101)', 'whole foods plant based diet', 'forks over knives', 'earthlings', 'environment', 'planet', 'cruelty', 'vegetarian', 'pcrm', 'happy cow', 'livestock and climate change', 'Should YOU Go Vegan? Bananiac Responds to Russell Brand The Trews']
description:
This is a response video to "Should I Become A Vegan? Russell Brand The Trews Comments (E101)" - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sblLEZXDcc0

In a recent video of the trews by Russell Brand, he says that he is a vegetarian and that he is thinking about going vegan. In this video, bananiac presents facts as to why Russell Brand, or anyone else for that matter, should go vegan. 

There are many reasons to go vegan. The first is for your health. Watch the documentary "Forks Over Knives" to learn more about the science behind a whole food plant based diet and how it can prevent and reverse major chronic diseases. If you want to sustain a long and happy life, keep your fat/oil and salt intake low, focus on starches & fruits, and eat AS MUCH AS YOU WANT!!!

Another reason to go vegan is for the environment. The meat and dairy industry is the number 1 consumer of water and grain consumption, which could essentially feed those who die from hunger and thirst every day. Animal agriculture is also the largest producer of greenhouse gas emission and contributor to global warming.

The most selfless reason to go vegan is for the ethics of animal welfare and a cruelty-free lifestyle. Eating meat, dairy, eggs, fish, etc. contribute to the suffering and death of millions of animals around the world DAILY! To learn more about this ruthless industry, please watch the documentary "Earthlings"

Going vegan is one of the best decisions you can make. Who has ever regretted eating yummy plant foods while saving the animals and the planet??

title: Tombul Hindi'nin Efsane Muffin tarifi
tags: ['Çılgın Şef', 'Bemaddy', 'Çocuk yemekleri', 'Çocuk tarifleri', 'Muffin tarifi', 'anne baba çocuk']
description: Tombul Hindi diğer kümes hayvanlarıyla birlikte bir çiftlikte yaşarmış. İnek, kuzu, tavuk, horoz, at ve diğer hayvanların yanı sıra kuzeni Gösterişli Tavuskuşu da aynı çiftlikteymiş. Gösterişli Tavuskuşu'nun yelpaze gibi açılan rengarenk tüyleri varmış. Tombul Hindi'nin de yelpaze gibi açılan tüyleri varmış ama onunkiler o kadar gösterişli değilmiş. Üstelik, Tombul Hindi biraz da şişmanmış. Çiftlikte hep Gösterişli Tavuskuşu'nun güzelliği  konuşuluyormuş... Tombul Hindi bu duruma çok içerlemiş. Bir gün düşünmüş, taşınmış ve öyle bir şey yapmalıyım ki benim şu kuzene bir ders olsun demiş. Veee ne mi yapmış???... Hemen mutfağa koşmuş, Çılgın Şef'I aramış ve ondan aldığı tarifle muhteşem bir muffin pişirmiş. Pişirdiği Muffin'in lezzetli kokusu bütün çiftliği sarmış. Bu kekten yiyebilmek için bütün hayvanlar sıraya girmiş! O günden sonra Gösterişli Tavuskuşu'nun tüylerinden çoook Tombul Hindi'nin Efsane Muffin tarifi konuşulur olmuuuş...

7 월 Areia에 의해 리믹스 생산 Vodge Diper

Release Date/릴리스 날짜: 2012.7.26
Genre/장르: House (Progressive/Swedish/Bigroom)
Tempo/템포: 128bpm
Key/음조: D (10B)
Subtitles timing by devilbryan1

This is another sweet takeover from Vodge Diper, throwing away my never to be finished remix and starting over again coming up with this great Swedish House result! The song's form doesn't follow the standard verse-chorus-bridge format so VD did a great job with taking these vocals and integrating in his beats.

In case you have missed my multiple posts on Facebook and Twitter, the last few weeks has been the most exciting days since I've been working at Trophy Entertainment (CHI CHI, Andamiro, Ali, Wax) on original KPOP songs as well as official remixes. The two first works will be the new Andamiro's single which I had the luck to work with legendary producers such as Choi Jun Young and Yuta and then there will be the official remix for CHI CHI's Love Is Energy where there is a teaser picture on my website featuring the girls.

This is pretty much my kickstart into official kpop music and I own it all to you: 18,000 wonderful subscribers that remix by remix have been pushing me further and further. I therefore have self-funded the remaining remixes on the list and I won't be asking from you to fund any more remixes. Instead you can always support my work by generic donations or by watching/purchasing KPOP songs that I'm involved with.

Thank you everybody, it has been a wonderful trip and it will continue just with a different course. No more calm seas and building castles on the sand: This time we are going straight to the dragons. I hope your support will continue on the official releases!

title: Samsung Galaxy S5 Layblock Vegetable Tanned Leather Case
description:
This is Hot!

Check out the website,
http://www.zoarah.com/

• Brand: Unikko/Layblock

• Material: Italian Vegetable tanned leather, Suede

  * What is Vegetable tanned leather?

It is tanned using Tannin and other ingredients found in vegetable matter, tree bark, and other such sources. It is supple and brown in color, with the exact shade depending on the mix of chemicals and the color of the skin. Vegetable-tanned leather is not stable in water; it tends to discolor, and if left to soak and then dry it will shrink and become less supple and harder. In hot water, it will shrink drastically and partly gelatinise, becoming rigid and eventually brittle. 

• Origin: Korea

• Condition: Brand new

• Features:

1. Layblock Italian vegetable tanned leather cases are renowned worldwide for their exquisite quality and workmanship. The Layblock Daily Easy Classic Case is manufactured from luxury vegetable tanned leather and is specially designed for the Galaxy S5, with every case being carefully cut, assembled and stitched by hand to perfectly complement the aesthetic Samsung Galaxy S5

2. With this case you can leave your wallet at home thanks to the three credit card slots and a money pockets. This makes it the perfect case for when you're popping out to the shops, going out in the evening or even if you just prefer to travel light

3. Designed specifically for the Samsung Galaxy S5, this case offers a perfect fit for your device. It also features a cut-out for the camera, and an open base so you don't need to take the phone out of the case to charge or synchronise it. All buttons are also still accessible when the phone is in the case

title: It's Complicated - Official Trailer (HD)
description: Jane is the mother of three grown kids, owns a thriving Santa Barbara bakery/restaurant and has—after a decade of divorce—an amicable relationship with her ex-husband, attorney Jake. But when Jane and Jake find themselves out of town for their sons college graduation, things start to get complicated. An innocent meal together turns into the unimaginable—an affair. With Jake remarried to the much younger Agness, Jane is now, of all things, the other woman. Caught in the middle of their renewed romance is Adam, an architect hired to remodel Janes kitchen. Healing from a divorce of his own, Adam starts to fall for Jane, but soon realizes hes become part of a love triangle. Should Jane and Jake move on with their lives, or is love truly lovelier the second time around? Its--complicated.

description: Was looking forward to a buggy in 8-10 knots at Sandy Point but the wind did not cooperate!  With only 3-4 knots straight down the beach I settled for a static flying session of the Nasa Star 2 4m.  I get a laugh out of nose diving this into the ground (not a good idea with a foil) and launching it backwards.  Don't know quite how it does that as it's not a four line kite......A very easy to control, yet powerful kite that's pretty hard to break makes it excellent for anyone.  Extremely good in gusty conditions too.  From Born-Kite.de

tags: ['W�rmetauscher sp�len', 'Renault 19', 'Wärmetauscher', 'Heizung', 'Heizungskühler', 'Kühlwasser', 'Kühlkreislauf', 'Kühlwasser braun', 'braunes Kühlwasser', 'rostiges Kühlwasser', 'Rost im Kühlwasser', 'Wärmetauscher verstopft', 'Wärmetauscher spülen', 'Kühlwasserkreislauf spülen', 'Kühler spülen', 'Heizung geht nicht', 'keine Warmluft', 'heizt nicht', 'Heizung zu schwach']
description:
Bei älteren Fahrzeugen (wie hier im Beispiel 
Renault 19) kann es vorkommen, dass 
sich über die Jahre der Wärmetauscher 
der Heizung mit "Rostschlamm" zu setzt.
Ein Tausch des Wärmetauschers ist 
meistens zu teuer. Das Spülen kann eine leichte
Verbesserung der Heizleistung bringen.

►Infos, ERSATZTEILE & WERKZEUGE zum Video findest Du hier:
http://box6014.webnode.com/ifa-youngtimer/warmetauscher-der-heizung-spulen-am-renault-19/

Fehlerbild:
-Innenraum wird nicht warm
-Warmluft kommt nur bei niedriger
Lüfter-Drehzahl
-Warmluft wird kälter, wenn Lüfter-
Drehzahl erhöht wird
-Warmluft kommt erst bei höherer
Motordrehzahl

Um etwas länger Freude an der Heizleistung 
zu haben, sollte nicht nur der 
Wärmetauscher gespült werden. 
Ebenso sind alle anderen Teile und 
Leitungen im gesamten Kühlkreislauf 
von der braunen Pest befallen und 
sollten ausgiebig gespült werden.

Für das alte Kühlwasser müssen die 
örtlichen Entsorgungsvorschriften 
beachtet werden.
Zum Spülen wird klares Wasser genommen.
Vor dem Kauf der neuen Kühlflüssigkeit 
muß nachgeschlagen werden, welche 
die richtige für deinen Motortyp ist 
(Google wird es wissen).


 
//////////////////////////////////////////

Voraussetzungen und Qualifikation:
Meine Videos befähigen nicht gleich jeden, Arbeiten an Fahrzeugen durchzuführen. 
Für viele Arbeiten ist etwas Schrauber-Erfahrung und eine Werkzeug-Grundausrüstung nötig, sowie handwerkliches Geschick, technisches Verständnis und Kfz-Grundwissen.

Einige meiner Videos (Zielgruppe: Hobby-Schrauber) sind bewusst weniger detailiert ausgeführt, um "Laien" nicht zum kopflosen Gefriemel zu verleiten und Schrauber nicht mit Standard-Tüdelkram zu zu müllen. Meine Videos sind keine Arbeitsanweisungen sondern Infomaterial um einen Überblick über den Arbeitsumfang zu erhalten. Somit kannst Du selbst entscheiden, ob Du Dir die Arbeit zutraust oder in die Werkstatt fährst.

title: dung lam anh dau.MINH VUONG
description:
Đừng nhìn anh bằng ánh mắt xa lạ.
Xin đừng nhìn anh bằng ánh mắt vô tình.
Đã bao ngày qua, em cứ lạnh lùng trốn tránh anh.
Rồi khi gặp nhau sao em hờ hững vô tâm.

Có phải em đã không còn yêu anh như ngày nào.
Có phải em đã yêu một người hơn anh.
Sao em nỡ lừa dối đánh mất tình cảm hai chúng ta.
Để khi anh nhận ra thì sự thật đã quá đau lòng.

ĐK:

Vì ngày hôm qua anh đã nhìn thấy em ôm hôn một người.
Lòng đau xót khi anh nhận ra sự thật sao quá trái ngang.
Anh đã thẩn thờ và gục ngã trước nỗi đau vô bờ.
Như muốn cào xé tan nát trái tim anh.

Từng giọt nước mắt cũng không thể xóa được hết những nỗi đau này.
Chẳng lẽ em xem như tình yêu chỉ là trò chơi đắng cay.
Sẽ có một ngày em nhận ra.
Chẳng có ai yêu em thật lòng như anh

title: América 3 x 3 Novorizontino - Série A3 - Melhores momentos
description:
A partida entre Grêmio Novorizontino e América rendeu fortes emoções na noite desta quarta-feira, 19. Os seis gols marcados, três para cada equipe, dão uma boa ideia do que foi este jogo, importante para os donos da casa, que queriam se afastar da zona de degola, e para os visitantes que queriam se aproximar do líder Rio Preto.
O Grêmio chegou com vontade e com menos de cinco minutos já havia criado várias boas chances de gol. Mas o placar só foi aberto mesmo aos 26 minutos, quando Pereira fez um passe perfeito para Selmir, que encarou o goleiro Kevin e marcou.
Mas aos 32, numa confusão na área, Bismark se aproveitou da falha da zaga e empatou.
Para o técnico Guilherme Alves, o estilo de jogo, aberto com as duas equipes no ataque, já era esperado. O treinador também lamentou a falha do zagueiro Da Silva. "Tomar um gol assim é o que me deixa mais triste", afirmou.
Na volta para o segundo tempo, Zé Augusto deu lugar a Pedrão. O América foi para cima e, numa cobrança de falta, Pilo, camisa 10, virou para os donos da casa, quando o cronômetro marcava 16 minutos. Aos 32 Naldinho ampliou cobrando pênalti e o Grêmio diminuiu aos 34, com o zagueiro Da Silva.
O jogo ainda reservava fortes emoções. Kleison, camisa 6 que foi substituído ainda no primeiro tempo, acabou expulso do banco de reservas do América por reclamações. No minuto seguinte, Pereira fez novo cruzamento e Guilherme Queiroz empatou, aos 46 minutos. 
O volante Carlinhos tomou seu segundo amarelo no jogo e acabou expulso e o juiz Renato Canadinho, que queria mais jogo, mandou seguir. Aos 52 minutos o árbitro marcou pênalti a favor do América, mas o goleiro Yuri, fez uma defesa espetacular para fechar o placar em 3 a 3. A defesa de Yuri fez a torcida do Tigre do Vale comemorar como se fosse gol e até o técnico Guilherme Alves entrou em campo para abraçar o jogador. "A gente sabe que esta é uma equipe como poucas, unida e mais uma vez mostrou isso em campo. Cometemos erros, vamos trabalhar para não acontecer mais E nós vamos buscar a classificação e o acesso", afirmou Yuri.
 
O resultado da 13ª rodada deixa o Grêmio Novorizontino com 23 pontos, em terceiro lugar na classificação, atrás do São José, que goleou o Independente e foi a 24, e do Rio Preto, líder isolado com 27. Para o técnico, Guilherme Alves, mais uma vez o time mostrou que tem forte poder de reação e que já sabia que o América seria um adversário difícil.
Na próxima rodada, dia 22, o Grêmio receberá a Votuporanguense no estádio Dr. Jorge Ismael de Biasi.

title: Whisker Haven Tales - A Dreamy-ful Birthday - Official Disney Junior UK HD
description:
Berry, Pumpkin, and Treasure are preparing a birthday party surprise for Dreamy! While Berry is busy making the cake, Pumpkin and Treasure argue about what kind of party to throw for their sleepy kitten friend.

Treasure, the adorable kitten of Princess Ariel makes her first journey to Whisker Haven to help Pumpkin and the other Palace Pets when the bubble bath overflows into the ballroom.

For more fun and games from all of your favourite shows, head over to: 
http://www.disneyjunior.co.uk/

Want more updates and exclusive goodies? Like our Facebook page:
http://www.facebook.com/DisneyJuniorUK

Disney Junior brings you an all new animated series of shorts: Whisker Haven Tales with the Palace Pets! The Palace Pets venture into the fairytale kingdom of Whisker Haven where they discover the beauty of kindness, the glamor of serving others and the royal heart of friendship as they fulfill their duties as royal pets.

WHISKER HAVEN TALES

Enter the secret magical animal kingdom of Whisker Haven and meet the Palace Pets Treasure, Pumpkin, Petite, Sultan, Dreamy and Berry, the beloved and cute pets belonging to all your favourite Disney Princesses! 

Join the Palace Pets in Whisker Haven Tales, a cute animated series following the fairy-tale adventures of Treasure and her friends where they discover the beauty of kindness, the good in serving others and what true friendship is all about. With the help of Ms Featherbon, a hummingbird fairy who helps the Palace Pets fulfil their duties as royal pets.

So transport yourself to the magical realm of Whisker Haven for some seriously enchanting, fun-filled animal adventures in the Whisker Haven Tales 

TREASURE
Treasure is a little scarlet kitten with aqua blue eyes -  in fact she looks a little like her owner, Princess Ariel. Treasure is courageous and loves adventure, especially the ones that involve lots of water!

PUMPKIN
Pumpkin is Cinderella’s little white dancing Poodle puppy. She is always polite and exudes elegance. She loves to twirl around and you will always find her on the dancefloor at royal balls!

PETITE
Petite is a little brown pony belonging to Princess Belle. Petite loves to have adventures, she’s full of determination and never gives up.

SULTAN
Sultan is a cute little orange tiger cub belonging to Princess Jasmine. He may be small but he has huge courage and is very brave. He is a furry ball of energy with a tiger tail!

DREAMY
Dreamy is Aurora’s sweet little sleepy kitten who is always ready to catch a catnap.


BERRY
Berry is Snow White’s shy and beautiful bunny. Berry is kind, and very keen on food, she loves to bake delicious treats.

MISS FEATHERBON
Ms. Featherbon is a blue hummingbird fairy and the magical gatekeeper of Whisker Haven. She is very fond of the Palace Pets and is always on hand to offer them advice if they need it.

title: Let's Play: Doom 2 (Map03) - The Gantlet
description:
A playthrough of "The Gantlet" (Map03) of Doom II: Hell on Earth for PC, played through GLBoom. 100% kills, 100% secrets (Max-Kill).

We're greeted by a new enemy here. One of the two "glass cannons" introduced in this game, he's highly annoying and can mow you down with lightning speed, especially in large numbers. This is the ONLY enemy where Invisibility Spheres are useful, and that's saying something!

As far as the map goes, it's very standard. Hardest secret to reach is the one in the room where you meet the Heavy Weapons Dude, or Chaingunner. Where you have to make that awkward jump into the hole. It can be tricky due to the sheer number of Chaingunners, but if they're giving you problems... you'll be in for a world of hurt later.

title: How To: Dribble Jab Step Basketball Move | Move Used By Kevin Durant, Damian Lillard & More
tags: ['jab step basketball', 'jab step', 'jab step jump shot', 'jab step moves', 'jab step step back', 'what is a jab step in basketball', 'how to do a jab step', 'how to execute a jab step', 'jab step basketball video', 'jab step basketball youtube', 'jab step dribble', 'jab step in basketball', 'Basketball Moves', 'Kevin Durant (Celebrity)', 'Damian Lillard (Award Winner)', 'basketball jab step', 'Basketball (Interest)', 'augie johnston', 'baller boot camp']
description:
Here I breakdown how to execute the dribble jab step basketball move.

http://BallerBootCamp.com/sww -- Free Workout

http://instagram.com/ballerbootcamp  -- Follow me

http://BallerBootCamp.com/Itunes - Sub To My Podcast

Here is the complete breakdown on our website:

http://ballerbootcamp.com/dribble-jab-step-basketball-move

The dribble jab step basketball move is an advanced move for advanced players only.

But I'm guessing that no matter if you are 8 years old or 21 years old you feel like you are an advanced player.

I guess the word advanced is pretty relative.

An 8 year old really could be advanced for his age, but is still too young to shoot three pointers and execute complex moves.

So when I say advanced here I'm talking about players who are either playing in college or who will be playing in college in 1-2 years.

The dribble jab move has become more and more popular as of late.

Of course, some players have used it in the past, but it seems like in the past 5 years or so we are starting to see it more often.

Here is a list of some of the players I've seen use this:

    -Kevin Durant
    -Damian Lillard
    -Derrick Rose
    -Stephen Curry

If you can think of any other players please leave them in the comment section.

The dribble jab step does one thing...

Creates space.

So you can use this move to get off a shot or to setup your defender.

Once you are able to create that space you can now control your defender easier.

If they react and close that space you should work to counter and blow by them.

If they don't close that space then you are free to shoot.

Here is the step by step breakdown for when the defense does not close that space:

   1. Face up against your defender.

   2. Turn and jab hard while pounding at the same time.

   3. Push off your inside foot into a step back

   4. Take your open shot

So as you can see you can create a lot of space with that especially when the defense reacts to your jab, drops their hands, and retreats.

Here is a quick little video showing Damian Lillard using this move in the NBA.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2afjC0nKegE

Ok, I hope you liked the dribble jab step basketball move breakdown and if you enjoyed it check out my channel for a ton more.

Here is the complete breakdown on our website:

http://ballerbootcamp.com/dribble-jab-step-basketball-move

description:
Assemblage é um processo artístico no qual a composição tridimensional se faz combinando objetos não artísticos (por vezes encontrados). 
Estes objetos compartilham a característica de não terem sido feitos com uma estética artística, apenas foram redescobertos pelos artistas, que os incorporam às suas obras de maneira conjunta ou individual, para exprimirem uma mensagem ou emoção.
Assemblage é o primo tridimensional do Collage. A origem da palavra (no seu sentido artístico) remonta ao princípio da década do 1950.
*
Assemblage is an artistic process in which a three-dimensional artistic composition is made from putting together non artistic (maybe found) objects.
These objects share the characteristic of not being made with aesthetics, they were rediscovered by the artists that incorporate them in their art to express a message or emotion.
Assemblage is the tridimensional cousin of Collage. The origin of the word (in its artistic sense) can be traced back to the early 1950s.

title: حفر ابار المياة و انزال الفلاتر
description:
المجموعة الدو لية للمقاولات(ميريام)

نقوم بعمل الإستشارات والدراسات الهندسية لعمل وتنفيذ وتصميم محطات تحلية مياه الشرب لجميع الإحتياجات والانتاجيات و حفر ابار المياة والطلمبات
ونحن من أقوى الشركات العاملة فى مجال المياه والبيئة والتى تضم طاقم من الاداريين والاستشاريين والمهندسين على اعلى مستوى من الكفاءة بوضع خبراتها بين ايديكم فى جميع مجالات حفر ابار المياه والطلمبات بجميع انواعها.

*مجالات عمل الشركة:-

• تقوم الشركه بحفر ابار المياه الجوفيه أعماق من صفر الى 600متر عمق .

• توريد وتركيب طلمبات الاعماق بجميع انواعها و مشتملاتها .

* تورتوريد المواسير بجميع الاقطار الحديد و البلاستك .

. توريد وتركيب طلمبات الطاقة الشمسية .

محطات تحلية ومعالجة المياه
-- تحلية مياه المنزل لتصبح صالحة للشرب والإستخدام ( بدل تعبئة وشراء جوالين المياه المخزنة ).
-- تحلية مياه الآبار ومعالجتها لتصبح صالحة للشرب او الزراعه او الإستخدام .
-- تحلية مياه البحر ومعالجتها لتصبح صالحة للشرب او الزراعه او الإستخدام .
-- تكرير مياه الصرف الصحي ومعالجتها لتصبح صالحة للزراعة او الإستخدام .
-- تكرير مياه الصرف الصناعي ومعالجتها لتصبح صالحة للتدوير ونفس الإستخدام الصناعي ولتوفير المياه.
إن ميزة جهاز RO أنه يزيل جميع الأملاح المنحلة في الماء وذلك بنسب متفاوتة تصل إلى 99 % لبعض العناصر.
وتعتبر محطة التحلية التي نقوم بانشائها من الأجهزة الحديثة المطابقة للمواصفات العالمية للتحلية والتي تعمل بنظام التناضح العكسي والضغط الإسموزي وتعمل على فصل الأملاح الذائبة في الماء . وذلك بقدرات إنتاجية مختلفة تصل الى الاف المترات المكعبة من الماء المحلى - وذلك بقدرة تحمل لأملاح المياه الخام بملوحة تصل إلى ( 50 - 000 ) TDSمالح فائق العناصر .. لتكون مياه صالحة للشرب الآدمي بنسبة تصل إلى 120 TDS .

title: Hot Can Self Heating Soup Demo and Review
tags: ['Survival food', 'Hiking food', 'MRE Alternative', 'Meals Ready To Eat', 'MRE', 'Camping Food']
description:
I have a Hot Can Self Heating Soup out on a hike at Camp Nelson Kentucky. Hot Can Self Heating Soup comes in different flavors; I review the tomato soup. The soup comes in a special can that contains it's on chemical heating which is activated by pressing on a button on the bottom of the can. It takes about 3 minutes to make a steaming hot soup.

For short hikes or hunting in a tree stand where building a fire or using a stove isn't convenient, Hot Can makes for a good option. However, for trips where you will need to bring enough food for many meals, Hot Can Soups will be heavy compared to alternatives.

title: Haven vs Kaz'rogal (World of Warcraft)
description:
Haven's third kill of the third boss in the Caverns of Time: Mount Hyjal raid instance.  A VERY simple fight.  We actually downed him on our first try on our first kill!  And yes, if you play DDR the song I chose should help reflect how easy this encounter was, heh.


Notes:

-The boss was pulled near Thrall so that he'd aggro.  Then the boss was moved toward the tauren warrior encampment.  The added dps helps a lot!

-Shadow resistance can make a difference in this fight!  I was only wearing my Black Temple neck plus my shadow prot buff and I was resisting his debuffs half the time.

-Healing isn't very intensive.  Raid-wide damage is very minimal with only the melee taking some damage from the boss' war stomps.  It's only when people start going OOM that player deaths start happening.

-I generally used Greater Heal (rank 2), Renews, and the occasional Circle of Healing to heal.

-Conserving mana is VERY important!  I only used spells when I needed to, then wanded the boss (pally had Judgement of Wisdom up).

-The boss was tanked by a protection spec warrior.

Enjoy the video? Subscribe! ► http://bit.ly/SubToSeaNanners

Wanna play? Click here: http://bit.ly/UYrlRu

What is Dead Space 3?

"Dead Space 3 pits player character Isaac Clarke against the Necromorphs, human corpses reanimated by the signal of an alien artifact known as the Marker. The Resource Integration Gear (RIG) suit returns, using holographic displays projected from the players' suit and weapons to display health and ammo count, respectively. In vacuum areas a timer will appear on the player's right shoulder, indicating how much oxygen that character has left before they suffocate.

In Dead Space 3, Isaac and Carver can roll and take cover to avoid attacks. This new ability was described by a Visceral Games developer as essential, as it "felt dumb/terrible not to have it" and that they have been "making Isaac more responsive", as they "want the horror to come from the terrible things that happen in the game; not from the horror that something is moving slowly towards you and you can't shoot it because the game controls like a piece of crap.  "The cover system is also described as "organic" in nature; for example, the player does not need to "walk up to certain tagged things and press the cover button; Clarke or Carver just does the action that is appropriate for the given situation."

Aside from the returning Necromorphs, Dead Space 3 features a large cast of new enemies. One example is the Waster, whose attacks change depending on how it is dismembered; while another is the Nexus, an insect-like giant that can crush or swallow people whole.  Other obstacles in Dead Space 3 include a new human enemy, Unitologist soldiers; and environmental hazards like falling machinery and a giant mining drill.

The bench weapon upgrade system from Dead Space and Dead Space 2 has been redesigned as a new upgrading system called the 'Weapons Bench'. Here, players are able to construct new weapons from parts gathered throughout the game. The bench provides two main frames to start with—a light one-hand frame and a heavy two-hand frame—and players can build new weapons and put two weapons together (for example, a plasma cutter and a flamethrower). Examples of weapon functions include an electric rivet gun and an incendiary buzzsaw launcher.  If a player does not want to build a weapon from scratch, they can choose from ready-made blueprints, including classic Dead Space and Dead Space 2 weapons. Built weapons can also be shared in co-op mode."

title: Handmade Portraits: Wood Mosaics
description:
Read the full article on Etsy's blog. http://www.etsy.com/storque/article/2588/ 

Robin and Kathy Tucker of Wood Mosaics stopped working in town back in 1986. After Robin's intricate wood-inlayed work was featured in The Best of Missouri Hands catalog and commissioned by Ralston Purina, they were on their way to full time crafting. Influenced by Amish quilt patterns, Robin's excellent woodworking uses exotic natural woods that range from Satinwood from Sri Lanka to Purpleheart from Central and South America. All of the wood is completely natural, with only a clear finish added to punctuate the beauty of the wood's innate color.

See more of the Tucker's beautiful designs at their Etsy shop:

description:
Guilderton is a small holiday town 97km north of Perth in Western Australia. The town is situated at the mouth of the Moore River which in Summer time is blocked from flowing into the Indian Ocean by a narrow sand bar. The only accommodation in the town is the Guilderton Caravan Park which is totally booked out every week-end. Long week-ends and summer holiday periods are booked out 1 year in advance.
The main visitor activities are: boating; kayaking, swimming & fishing.

title: Wühlmäuse fangen | landwirt.com
tags: ['landwirt.com', 'landwirtcom', 'Landvideo', 'Landwirtschaft', 'Der fortschrittliche Landwirt', 'Wühlmaus', 'Wühlmäuse', 'Wühlmäuse fangen', 'Wühlmaus fangen', 'Wühlmäuse bekämpfen', 'Wühlmäuse vertreiben', 'Wühlmausfalle', 'Mausefalle', 'Wolfsche Zangenfalle', 'Zangenfalle', 'Wühlmäuse täten', 'Maulwurf fangen', 'Maulwurf vertreiben', 'Maulwurffalle', 'Wolfsche Wühlmausfalle', 'Zangenfalle Wühlmaus', 'Zangenfalle richtig aufstellen', 'Zangenfallen', 'Maus fangen', 'Mausefalle aufstellen', 'Mäuse bekämpfen', 'Mäuse fangen', 'Mäuse vertreiben']
description:
Wühlmäuse fressen die Wurzeln der Futterpflanzen auf den Wiesen. Die ausgeworfenen Erdhaufen verschlechtern Narbendichte, Futterertrag und tierische Leistungen. Michael Hauer erklärt im Interview mit LANDWIRT Redakteurin Christina Vetta, wie Wühlmäuse gefangen werden. Einen ausführlichen Artikel zum Thema findet ihr in der LANDWIRT Ausgabe 11/2015.

Gratis Probeheft bestellen: http://www.landwirt.com/youtube
Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/landwirtcom
Gebrauchte Landmaschinen: http://www.landwirt.com/gebrauchte/Gebrauchtmaschinenmarkt.html
Kleinanzeigen: http://www.landwirt.com/Kleinanzeigen/Kleinanzeigen.html
LANDWIRT Forum: http://www.landwirt.com/Forum/Forum.html
Traktor-WM: http://www.landwirt.com/traktorwm/intro/

Der LANDWIRT ist Österreichs führende Fachzeitschrift für Landwirte. Das Heft erscheint zweimal im Monat und behandelt alle Themen der Landwirtschaft. Die steigende Auflagezahl belegt, dass sich der LANDWIRT im gesamten deutschsprachigen Raum zunehmender Beliebtheit erfreut.

Immer mehr Landwirte informieren sich online. Landwirt.com liefert tagesaktuelle Meldungen, Bilder und Videos aus dem In- und Ausland. Ein umfangreicher Marktplatz für Gebrauchtmaschinen und Kleinanzeigen, Termine und ein Forum runden das Angebot ab. Mit der LANDWIRT App für iPhones, Android-Handys und Tablets lassen sich diese Serviceleistungen auch jederzeit unterwegs nutzen, kostenlos und unverbindlich.

Wer gerne im Gebrauchtmaschinenmarkt stöbert, dem sei das landwirt.com-Journal ans Herz gelegt! Das Heft erscheint zweimal im Monat und liefert ein umfangreiches Angebot an gebrauchten Traktoren und Landmaschinen in gedruckter Form nachhause.

Auch in den sozialen Medien ist der LANDWIRT präsent: Auf der Facebook-Seite liefern sich die Fans lebhafte Diskussionen. Auf YoutTube werden mehrmals pro Woche neue Videos aus allen Bereichen der Landwirtschaft veröffentlicht.

title: Tribute to Sonny Bill Williams
description:
Thanks to Rugby Dump for some scenes

Music: Fort Minor - Remember the Name

Sonny William 'Sonny Bill' Williams (born 3 August 1985) is a New Zealand rugby union player and former rugby league player. He is only the second person to represent New Zealand in rugby union after first playing for the country in rugby league. In rugby union he usually plays as a centre. He is particularly known in rugby league and rugby union for his ability to offload the ball in the tackle and, in rugby league, for his shoulder charges.

He started his professional rugby league career with the Canterbury Bulldogs in the Australian NRL. In 2008 he controversially left the Bulldogs mid-season to play rugby union with French club Toulon. In 2010 Williams signed with the New Zealand Rugby Union in an ultimately successful bid to play for the All Blacks at the 2011 Rugby World Cup. He played for Canterbury in the 2010 ITM Cup before being selected for the All Blacks' end of year tour in 2010, making his debut against England at Twickenham. He played for the Crusaders in the 2011 season of Super Rugby and will play for the Chiefs in the 2012 Super Rugby season. He was a member of the All Blacks squad that won the 2011 Rugby World Cup.

Since 2009 he has boxed four times, winning all four of his heavyweight bouts.

title: 2014 Dodge Durango SUV Walkaround Video Review w/ Chief Engineer Tom Burgess
tags: ['2014 Dodge Durango', 'dodge', 'Dodge Durango (Automobile Model)', 'Chrysler', 'suv', 'sport utility vehicle', 'walkaround', 'Review', 'engineer', 'car video', 'automobiles', 'automotive', 'cars', 'vehicles', 'new cars', 'car review', 'overview']
description:
The 2014 Dodge Durango sports some very exciting upgrades and updates that extend to both the interior and exterior of this SUV. The Durango's Chief Engineer Tom Burgess was kind enough to give Autobytel a thorough walkaround review of the 2014 model before it hits the showrooms. 

For the 2014 model year, Dodge is very excited to introduce some advanced technology features that cover 3 key areas including: fuel economy, electronics, and safety. The 2014 Dodge Durango comes equipped with 2 different powertrains. The first is a HEMI 5.7 liter V-8 that makes 360 horsepower and 390 lb-ft. of torque carrying with that a best-in-class towing ability. The second powertrain is a Pentastar 3.6 liter V-6 engine that makes 295 horsepower and 260 lb-ft. of torque. A new 8-speed transmission is now standard with both engines. The 2014 Durango offers best-in-class fuel economy with the V-6 netting 25 MPG on the highway and the V-8 netting 23 MPG on the highway.

The 2014 Dodge Durango is all about integrating the latest and greatest in technology and electronics. LED lighting is now standard on both the front and rear lights. The gauge cluster features a 7-inch TFT screen that is configurable. The Durango is packed with tons of cool tech including a huge Uconnect infotainment center. The gear shift is now located on the center console.

Safety wise there is a Forward Collision Mitigation System that alerts the driver. The Adaptive Cruise Control features a stop mechanism. Blind spot detection uses sensors in the rear fascia. This is the most technologically advanced Durango ever.

Find out more about the 2014 Dodge Durango
http://www.autobytel.com/dodge/durango/2014/?id=32972

More info about the game:
SPECIAL THANKS to the IndieGoGo contributors for helping make this game possible! I've already got updates planned in the future, but right now... I'm gonna take a nap. BLESS YOUR FACES!
When the Wizard of Darkness awakened, it was up to one man to defeat him. When that man was accidentally killed by one idiot, Tobuscus (or "person of extremely low intelligence" - gently put), the responsibility of becoming an AWESOME WIZARD fell onto him... by default!
GAME FEATURES:
- Play as Tobuscus and unlock new spells, wands, and potions as you level up!
- Battle tons of zombies, liches, and other evil creatures on 20 different maps across the Frozen Forest and Molten Mountains!
- Upgrade your Tower and Wizard Gear... or else you'll probably die!
- Draw ancient symbols on your screen to cast spells... ancient like, uhm... a triangle! Or a swirly circle-y thingy to create a huge tornado, allowing you to tilt your touchscreen Spellbook to tell the wind where to spin, hurling zombies into the outer atmosphere and almost out of the screen into REALITY ITSELF!
- Exclusive animated scenes that will bring you into the game in a way no other game has ever done as awesomely anywhere ever before!
- Launch your faithful dog that trusts you - Gryphon - from a cannon directly into battle to plant bombs and explode herds of zombies!
- Gabuscus is also in the game. (He made me include this.)

title: Welcome to the Kenton County School District++
description:
Welcome to the Kenton County School District, a system of Excellence!
We are so pleased that you have decided to join our professional family.  

Your selection as a member of our team speaks to your level of expertise and professional attributes.  We received over 400 applications for teaching and administrative positions.  

Your selection speaks to the value of what you have accomplished to date.  What you do from this point forward reflects the opportunities we provide you and what you take from these opportunities.   We expect a lot from our staff, but promise to provide you the tools and resources you need to be highly successful. From this point on you will become part of a very special community.

Kenton County School District leads Learning.  We want our employees to continue their learning and improving their craft and practice.  We are Innovative, creative in our thinking and always look for ways to improve the levels of student engagement and learning.

Our principals and administrators participate in the most current research based practices.  As leaders of learning, we offer significant opportunity to engage in mentoring, coaching and induction programs. This year you will be invited to attend learning sessions with other teachers who are new to our district.lease take advantage of these opportunities.  

Every employee is valued for their unique contributions.  You are part of a special learning community that stands above others for offering students a first class education. 

Welcome!  We are happy you have joined us. I look forward to meeting each of you at your school.   Have a fantastic year!

Grand Theft Auto V for PS4 features the all-new First Person Mode, giving players the chance to explore the incredibly detailed world of Los Santos and Blaine County in an entirely new way across both Story Mode and Grand Theft Auto Online. 

Los Santos: a sprawling sun-soaked metropolis full of self-help gurus, starlets and fading celebrities, once the envy of the Western world, now struggling to stay afloat in an era of economic uncertainty and cheap reality TV. Amidst the turmoil, three very different criminals risk everything in a series of daring and dangerous heists that could set them up for life.

Grand Theft Auto V for PS4 also includes Grand Theft Auto Online, the ever-evolving Grand Theft Auto universe. Explore the vast world or rise through the criminal ranks by banding together to complete Jobs for cash, purchase properties, vehicles and character upgrades, compete in traditional competitive modes, or create new content to play and share with the Grand Theft Auto community. 

All new content and gameplay created and released since the launch of Grand Theft Auto Online including new Jobs, an arsenal of new weapons, scores of new vehicles, new properties and player customizations will also be available in Grand Theft Auto Online for PS4. In addition, the current community of players will have the ability to transfer their Grand Theft Auto Online characters and progression to their choice of PlayStation 4, Xbox One or PC.

Matthijs Breukhoven speelt Bach op het orgel van R.C. Capella te Capelle aan den IJssel.

Matthijs Breukhoven werd geboren op 17 januari 1992 en volgde zijn eerste pianolessen op de SKVR muziekschool te Rotterdam. Daarna kreeg hij vele jaren les op piano en orgel van organist Frank J. van Wingerden. Sinds 2009 ontvangt Matthijs zijn orgellessen in de Grote of St. Janskerk in Schiedam van organist Arjen Leistra. Sinds 2005 is Matthijs vaste registrant  van zijn vader en bespeelde daardoor ook vele orgels in binnen- en buitenland. 
Matthijs is organist van de Verrijzeniskerk te Rotterdam en de Ark te Krimpen aan den IJssel

title: ΧχΧ η συνέχεια
OSOBNÍ VOZY ČD #2 - Bdt279, Bdt280
description:
Vozy Bdt279 a Bdt280, obě řady číslované v intervalu 50 54 21-08, jsou řadami velkoprostorových osobních vozů z vozového parku Českých drah. Všechny tyto vozy (001--195 a 196--395) vyrobila v letech 1986 až 1991 moravskoslezská Vagónka Studénka pod označením Bte (vozy Bdt279 měly do roku 1990 přechodné značení Btme). Po rozpadu Československa připadla Českým drahám zhruba polovina těchto vozů.
Jsou to neklimatizované osobní vozy se skříní typu UIC-Y o délce 24 500 mm. Mají podvozky GP 200 vybavené kotoučovými brzdami. Jejich nejvyšší povolená rychlost je 120 km/h. Vozy již byly dodány pouze s elektrickým topením.
Vnější nástupní dveře jsou zalamovací, mezivozové jsou manuálně posuvné do strany. Vozy mají polospouštěcí okna. Vozy Bdt280 mají podélné prolisy na střeše.
Interiér vozu je rozdělen na dva velké velkoprostorové oddíly, z nichž jeden má šest a druhý pět fiktivních oddílů. Celkem mají 88 míst k sezení realizovaných jako dvojmístné lavice potažené červenou koženkou v uspořádání 2 + 2.
Nátěr je přes okna zelený a zbytek bílý, nově se vozy lakují do modro-bílého stylu od studia Najbrt.
V letech 2008 a 2009 byl do devíti vozů Bdt279 dosazen centrální zdroj energie (CZE), a tyto vozy byly přeznačeny na řadu Btee289.
V letech 2011 až 2013 bylo 32 vozů Bdt279 a 2 vozy Btee289 v Pars nova Šumperk zmodernizováno na řídicí vozy Bfhpvee295. Ve vozech bylo vytvořeno řídicí stanoviště ve stylu lokomotivy 380. Kromě toho byl i kompletně zmodernizován interiér vozu, byl doplněn CZE, klimatizace, vakuové WC, zásuvky 230 V, audio-vizuální informační systém, nové předsuvné dveře, zvýšení rychlosti na 140 km/h. Celková cena modernizace činila více jak jednu miliardu korun (přibližně 31 milionů Kč za vůz).
Z těchto vozů se mimo jiné plánuje přestavba na řadu ABpee347 a také modernizace stávajících vozů. Zakázku, kterou ČD zadala 26.7.2011, vyhrála polská firma PESA Bydgoszcz.  Výběrové řízení snížilo cenu rekonstrukce z původních 270 milionů Kč (18 milionů Kč za vůz) na 191 milionů Kč (12 milionů Kč za vůz). Všechny vozy by měly být dodány nejpozději v létě 2014. V roce 2013 uzavřely České dráhy smlouvu na modernizaci 26 vozů Bdt279 s firmou KOS Krnov. Vozy při modernizaci získají nový interiér, CZE, předsuvné dveře ovládané tlačítky, přemostění záchranné brzdy a zásuvky 230 V. Zároveň bude maximální rychlost zvýšena na 140 km/h. Naopak nezískají ani klimatizaci, ani uzavřený systém WC. Celková cena rekonstrukce je 219 milionů Kč (8,5 milionu Kč za vůz).

Vozy lze potkat na některých rychlících (převážně v jižní části republiky) a dále na spěšných a osobních vlacích.

title: Superfoods - Green Tea Tips & Tricks
description:
1. Don't throw your tea leaves away after using them. Traditionally, people re-brew with the same leaves a few times in a 3-4 hour span. If you have high quality tea, your brew will be flavorful long after the first cup. 
2. If plain green tea isn't, well, your cup of tea, experiment with flavors. To reap health benefits, make sure you're still working with a green tea, and that it just has added flavors like "green tea with honey" or "green tea with ginger."
3. Don't steep your green tea longer than 3 minutes or it'll be bitter rather than flavorful. 
4. Got a bunch of green tea bags lying around? Save them for your next sunburn. Wet them in cool water and apply them directly to the burn. They'll sooth your skin and help it heal. 
5. Green tea absorbs odors around it.  If you get something stinky on your hands, rub some green tea on them. It's a great reason not to throw out old tea. Even when it doesn't taste good anymore, it works as a natural deodorant. 

ABOUT SUPERFOODS:

This weekly show spotlights super healthy foods and shows viewers how to incorporate them into their everyday diets. Get the skinny on everything from kale to pomegranates, learn delicious and easy recipes, and pick up tricks on how to add these super foods into the dishes you already love.

title: Fab 5 Sports Cars @ Detroit Auto Show 2015
tags: ['Auto Show (Event)', 'Sports Car (Automotive Class)', 'Automobile (TV Genre)', 'detroit auto show', 'Ford Mustang (Automobile Model)', 'Shelby Mustang (Automobile Model)', 'acura nsx', 'Alfa Romeo (Automobile Company)', 'Chevrolet Corvette (Automobile Model)', 'Cadillac CTS-V (Automobile Model)', 'car video', 'automobiles', 'automotive', 'cars', 'vehicles', 'new cars', 'car review', 'abtl', 'autobytel', 'horsepower', 'sportscar', 'sports car', 'muscle car', 'hot rod', 'v-8']
description:
http://www.autobytel.com/auto-shows/united-states/detroit/?id=32972 Today, we’re talking Sports Cars, starting with Ford. The 2015 Mustang GT350 is a special edition of the all-new Mustang specifically designed to out-handle the already-capable Mustang GT.  It’s equipped with enormous brakes, unique aerodynamic body work formed out of exotic materials, and a magnetically-adjustable suspension.  It also boasts a launch control system, standard six-speed manual transmission, and a 5.2-liter V-8 that churns out more than 500 horsepower.

We featured the 2016 Shelby GT350 in our Fab Five from the LA Auto Show, and here in Detroit, the Ford Shelby GT350R turns up the volume on everything we liked in LA. It’s 130 lbs lighter than its already svelte sibling and under the hood you get the same 5.2-liter V-8 with 500+ horsepower.  Ford stripped everything you don’t need on a race track from the GT350R to shed pounds. 
 
Acura has teased us forever with the NSX concept, and the 2016 Acura NSX production model doesn’t disappoint. It boasts call-outs to its first-generation sports car predecessor as well as design cues from the current Acura language.  The NSX looks every inch the modern supercar it’s intended to be. It features a trio of electric engines – two motivating the front axle, and one at the rear – that work together with a twin-turbo 3.5-liter V-6 that generates 550 horsepower. 

The only thing better than a mid-engine sports coupe is a mid-engine roadster - at least, that's the philosophy guiding the new 2015 Alfa Romeo 4C Spider.  The Spider drops the top on the well-received 4C Coupe, and we like the exciting results as much as we anticipate driving it. Under the hood, it’s got a 237 horsepower, 1.75-liter turbocharged four-cylinder engine.  It also comes with a carbon fiber tub and minimal modifications to its body structure to accommodate the fabric top. 
 
Combine a memorable Cadillac body with a Corvette Z06 engine that generates a whopping 640 horsepower, and you’ve got the Cadillac CTS-V.  It gets those horses from its 6.2-liter supercharged V-8, with 630 lb.-ft. torque, with an 8-speed auto transmission with paddle shifters.  Inside, you’ll find Recaro sport seats, carbon fiber trim, and plenty of gadgets, including a front camera and lane keep assist.  The CTS-V hits dealer lots in late summer, and it is well worth the wait.

This is Michelle Naranjo with Autobytel and that’s your Fab Five Sports Cars of the 2015 Detroit Auto Show.

title: Americano vende terrenos da Lua em Portugal
description:
Dennis Hope, um americano que se nomeou Presidente do Governo Galáctico, está em Portugal para vender terrenos na Lua «com vista para a Terra», um negócio que começou há mais de 20 anos e parece render-lhe milhões 

O norte-americano deu hoje uma conferência de imprensa num luxuoso hotel de Lisboa, para inaugurar a Embaixada Lunar em Portugal, um espaço na Internet onde qualquer um pode comprar «a sua propriedade com vista para a Terra» por 25 euros o hectare, cita-o a agência Lusa. 

O homem diz ser dono da «única agência imobiliária legalmente habilitada para vender terrenos no espaço» e já negociou certificados de propriedade com mais de 300 mil pessoas.

Entre os seus clientes estão personalidades políticas como Ronald Reagan, Jimmy Carter e George W. Bush e as estrelas de Hollywood Nicole Kidman, Clint Eastwood, Tom Cruise e John Travolta, garante o site www.embaixadalunar.com. 

A partir de hoje, também os portugueses podem adquirir uma propriedade por 25 euros o hectare, recebendo como garantia uma Escritura Lunar, uma Constituição, um mapa da propriedade, os Direitos Minerais e uma cópia da declaração original de detenção de propriedade da Lua.

«Não acredito que alguém pense que está realmente a adquirir um hectare da Lua», disse à Lusa o jurista da Associação de Defesa do Consumidor (Deco), Luis Salvador Pisco. 

«Em termos legais esta é uma situação em que as pessoas não poderão vir a invocar que houve uma burla, porque é demasiado evidente o que se está a passar. Suspeito que nenhum tribunal possa vir a dar razão» a futuros queixosos, alertou o jurista. 

No entanto, e de acordo com vários sites na internet, o negócio já rendeu mais de seis milhões de dólares (4,4 milhões de euros) e a Embaixada Lunar garante aos futuros clientes ser impossível vender o mesmo terreno a mais de uma pessoa, refere a Lusa. 

O lunático projecto que hoje chegou a Portugal começou em 1980, quando Hope foi ao registo de terras de San Francisco (Califórnia, Estados Unidos) e requereu a propriedade de todo o sistema solar, à excepção da Terra e do Sol. 

O americano reclamou a propriedade da Lua e de outros planetas baseando-se numa lei do Velho Oeste norte-americano do século XIX, «que concede a propriedade de terras devolutas as primeiro que as reclamar», explica o site. 

Dennis Hope enviou cartas aos governos dos Estados Unidos da América e da Rússia e à Assembleia-geral das Nações Unidas. Sem qualquer resposta às suas missivas, interpretou o silêncio como concordância e hoje afirma ser o «legítimo dono do sistema solar». 

«Não faz sentido um particular reivindicar para si a propriedade do sistema solar», sublinha o jurista da Deco, que desconfia da sanidade mental de Dennis Hope.

"Telejornal", RTP1, 11 de Maio de 2007

title: Lingfield 4-1 Fisher | The FA Cup Premliminary Round 04-09-11
description:
FATV - Whyteleafe FC, Surrey - 4th Sep 2011

Lingfield's fairytale season shows no signs of slowing down after they beat Fisher 4-1 to earn an away tie against Horsham in the First Qualifying Round.

The Sussex County League side have been catapulted into the news by the arrival of former Brighton, Brentford, Reading and Birmingham striker Nicky Forster and ex-West Ham and Blackburn defender Ian Pearce. And both players showed their class again on a memorable day for the club, which is based near East Grinstead and managed by David 'Dixie' Dean.

It was Forster, 37, who put his side on the way with an early penalty given for handball in the tie played at Whyteleafe FC.

And although Fisher equalised through Steve O'Donnell and were level at half-time, they couldn't hold on. Forster was on target again in the second half and Lingfield cruised to victory in the end despite some promising football from their visitors.

Forster has been influential for Lingfield ever since agreeing to play for his local team having announced his retirement from professional football.

The striker -- who was player-manager at Brentford last season -  also scored twice on his debut for his new club in the last round of The FA Cup against Hailsham Town.

This latest victory marked the end of Fisher's own fairytale return to tournament -- they were playing in the competition for the first time since the old Fisher Athletic went out of business in 2009. Highlights of this game will be on FATV on Monday.

Meanwhile, Leek Town earned a narrow 4-3 victory at Midland Alliance side Causeway, inflicting the home team's first defeat of the season. Leek went into a 3-0 lead and had to survive an inspired fight-back from the home side. Two goals from Matty Haddrell and further strikes from Devon Gibson and James McCarthy were enough for Neil Baker's side who now face Tipton Town at home. Causeway replied through Stuart How, Carl Martin and Scott Stevenson.

Wakefield made it through with a 1-0 victory over Thackley thanks to a goal from Luke Malcher whilst Aylesbury and North Leigh face a replay at Eynsham Park on Tuesday after drawing 0-0 in a hard-fought tie.

Grays Athletic posted a narrow 3-2 away win at AFC Dunstable -- who were playing in The FA Cup for the first time this season -  to reach the next round. They will host Aveley on Sunday 18 September. Their goals came from Louis Dennis, Junior Baker and Bradley Thomas - while Danny Bunce was sent off late on to make it a nervy finale.

Romford produced a thrilling 3-2 victory over Royston Town with Wola Odedoyin, Jack Barry and Abs Seymour scoring. Dalton O'Brien and Ryan Lockett replied for the Crows

Slough cruised through 3-1 against Binfield with two goals from Danny Burnell and one from Ben Abbey.

Chipstead won 2-1 at Epson & Ewell with goals from Jason Goodchild and Alex Wilks while Erith & Belvedere beat Selsey 4-1 with goals from Hinga Amara (2), Luke May and Andy Constable.

title: Tutorial #02 - Steam: left4dead 1&2 CUT zu UNCUT [Deutsch] [HD]
description:
In diesem Video zeige ich euch wie ihr aus eurem gecuttetem left4dead 1 und 2 ein Uncut left4dead machen könnt.

Deutsch:
Schritt 1:
öffne deinen left4dead bzw left4dead 2 ordner
("C:/Steam/steamapps/common/left 4 dead/* ")

Schritt 2:
öffne die datei "steam_appid.txt" mit dem editor
("C:/Steam/steamapps/common/left 4 dead/steam_appid.txt")

Schritt 3:
Trage dort die zahl "510" ein und speicher die datei ab.

Schritt 4:
gehe in den ordner left 4 dead/left4dead
("C:/Steam/steamapps/common/left 4 dead/left4dead/* ")

Schritt 5:
öffne die datei "steam.inf"
("C:/Steam/steamapps/common/left 4 dead/left4dead/steam.inf")

Schritt 6:
Trage hinter "appID" wieder die "510" ein und speicher ab.

Schritt 7:
mache dir eine Verknüpfung mit der left4dead.exe
("C:/Steam/steamapps/common/left 4 dead/left4dead.exe")
[nur wenn du von dieser verknüpfung left4dead startest wird es als uncut gestartet]

Jetzt bleibt mir nur noch zu sagen: "Viel Spaß beim ZoGgen"

[ Ihr könnt mit der geänderten appID nur mit leuten spielen die ihre appID auch geändert haben. Leute die es sich Cut/Uncut gekauft haben und die appID nicht verändern, mit denen könnt ihr nicht zusammen spielen.]

description:
Audio track tittel:Saltfjellet
n recent years, a programming phenomenon called Slow TV by Norwegian public broadcaster NRK2 has been very popular. Slow TV is characterized by hours and hours of continuous coverage of fixed cameras on a subject or event.

Past programs have included a seven-and-a-half hour train journey, a 134-hour coastal cruise, 12 hours of firewood burning and 18 hours of salmon fishing.

And now American producers are interested in this slow-moving entertainment.

Recently, US production company LMNO Productions acquired the rights to bring the Slow TV format stateside.

Also, NRK program "Northern Land train minute by minute" (Nordlandsbanen minutt for minutt) has been imported to be broadcasted in over 100 television stations online in the United States in new year.

Around 1.1 million television viewers watched the program "Nordlandsbanen minutt for minutt" about longest railway of Norway after Christmas last year.

title: Carmen - Oper von Georges Bizet
tags: ['Georges Bizet', 'Carmen', 'Deutsche Oper am Rhein', 'Rheinoper', 'Theater', 'Düsseldorf', 'Duisburg', 'Ralph Goertz', 'IKS Medienarchiv']
description:
Auch wenn Georges Bizets (1838--1875) „Carmen" bei ihrer Uraufführung am 3. März 1875 -- drei Monate vor dem Tode des Komponisten -- beim Pariser Publikum einen Skandal provozierte, entwickelte sie sich sehr bald zu einer der weltweit meistgespielten Opern. Bereits 1905 fand in Paris die tausendste Aufführung statt, und die schillernde Hauptfigur gilt bis heute als die Inkarnation des Männertraums schlechthin.

Prosper Mérimées 1845 veröffentlichte „Carmen"-Novelle brachte einen neuen Frauentyp in die zivilisierte Metropole Paris. Als Zigeunerin war Carmen mit ihrer wilden exotischen Schönheit das ideale Lustobjekt. Zugleich nimmt sie sich aber auch eine Freiheit zur Selbstbestimmung, die sich im 19. Jahrhundert nur Männer leisteten. Genau darin liegt ihr Reiz, aber auch ihr Verbrechen in den Augen der Gesellschaft -- und der Grund für ihre Ablehnung bei der Premiere. In Bizets Oper kann Carmen ihre Lebensphilosophie auf der Bühne offen ausleben. Was sie unter Liebe versteht, lässt sie bereits in der Habanera hören: die uneingeschränkte Freiheit der Gefühle, totale Freiheit auch von moralischen Bindungen. Das ist schließlich Carmens Verhängnis, sie verlangt, mit Liebe und Beziehung liberal umzugehen, wozu Don José nicht in der Lage ist -- von rasender Eifersucht getrieben bringt er seine mit dem Stierkämpfer Escamillo anbandelnde Geliebte um.

Im an die Bildwelten des spanischen Malers Francisco Goya gemahnenden Bühnenbild von Rifail Ajdarpasic arbeitete Regisseur Carlos Wagner in seiner im Januar 2011 an der Opéra National de Lorraine gefeierten Inszenierung die Freiheitsliebe Carmens und ihre Faszination für den mit ihr überforderten Sergeant Don José in düster-poetischen Bildern heraus. Die Fachzeitschrift Classique News schrieb über das große Finale: „Das letzte Bild ist unvergesslich und beweist den flammenden Einfallsreichtum eines großen Regisseurs, zwischen Wirklichkeit und Sehnsucht, Poesie und Expressionismus, Schatten und Licht."

***

CARMEN

Несколько слов о нашей команде.
Наш коллектив работает в двух направлениях.

Видео

title: Mugenkyo Taiko Drummers - Freak Music Sampler
tags: ['Mugenkyo Taiko Drummers', 'Mugenkyo Drummers', 'Mugenkyo', 'Taiko Drummers', 'hire Taiko Drummers', 'hire dojo drummers', 'dojo drummers', 'chinese drummers']
description:
More info and to book Mugenkyo - http://www.freakmusic.co.uk/bands/dojo_drummers

The Dojo Drummers are a dynamic and vibrant new taiko group, representing the Mugen Taiko Dojo, the UK's Centre for Taiko Drumming. Taiko drumming is a highly visual and exciting art form, and performances have thrilled audiences at every occasion.

Performances consist of both traditional taiko drum pieces and also modern compositions, which are energetic and highly choreographed. The Dojo Drummers use the full range of taiko drums, from a visually impressive one and a half metre diameter skin drum to small high-pitched drums for the fast and precise rhythms, and also various percussion, all top quality instruments imported especially from Japan.

All members of the group have trained intensively at the Dojo for several years, performing at various events including large sporting events such as the Worthington Cup Final at the Millennium Stadium in Cardiff, Scotland v. Japan International Rugby Match at Perth Stadium, Osprey v. Wasps New Stadium Opening in Swansea, and various outdoor festival appearances in UK and Ireland as well as many corporate events and private engagements across the UK.

A taiko drumming performance by the Dojo Drummers is a highly focused, perfectly synchronised, thrilling spectacle and an unforgettable experience.
